Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:39.32,eptitle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(298,25)}Episode 16\NSpring Wind Express
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.47,0:01:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! The lead pack is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.10,0:01:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tomomi-sempai after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did it! Move it, Yamagishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi-sempai's leading the pack by miles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's OK with you, right Remi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:09.99,announce,,0000,0000,0000,,The national high school marathon will start in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:14.22,announce,,0000,0000,0000,,Would all participants come to the starting point?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment of truth, huh Remi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get the picture of the moment you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last sprint was so awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you picked up the pace before the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so grate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't your legs hurt? I'll massage you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Matsunaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarashina-sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go. Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this Remi-sempai's?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remi gave them to me before she transferred schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She held the record of this race.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I heard she was the hope of the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had the same time as your's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Tomomi-chan had a tie record.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for you. A gift for the victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure? Isn't this important memory for you, Sarashina-sempai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want somebody who can run to her satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the shoes would be happy that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or don't you need a gift, because you didn't break the record?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Remi wouldn't mind if you have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky you, Tomomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome, Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nooo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga-san! Matsunaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that? Tomomi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing. Just felt dizzy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remi, what are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got time to kill, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm waiting for my date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kageura-sensei, it's no use putting on gadget like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now come and get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you underestimate your teacher's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remi, give your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:07:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat him, Remi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's awesome, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't met her since she transferred school. I wonder how she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the size?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems to be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, 2nd generation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomomi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi! Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My feet are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My feet are moving by themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Matsunaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling playful?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oy, Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi, stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, what have you been...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't run.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The goal is too far away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:09:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who's that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she really not joking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy. She just finished running a full marathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't do that as a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong, Tomomi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish I knew.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomomi, are you OK? Where are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The railway crossing by 3rd Street.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:12:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't. I can't run anymore. What do I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go for it, Remi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Break your record, will you Remi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How far do I have to run?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out. What's with you, Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on the back. We have to stop Tomomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sarashina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you had a secret like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I be a role model student without a secret or two?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Tomomi-chan headed this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She's heading that way. Straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twins are so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean you can say with certainty that she's going that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I envy twins!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we're heading the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know? You said to take a truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't run. I'm out of breath.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remi-sempai?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be expecting a new record.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Give your best shot, Remi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi-chan! Tomomi-chan, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, knock it off or you'll break down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't run. I'm out of breath.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, everybody.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's me... in that race...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remi, aren't you? It's been awhile. How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK. And you, Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'm so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:17:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're Mikage-chan and Tomomi-chan, one year junior to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With those shoes, this course, and at this spot.. You look miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remi, how could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know? I was so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Why did you leave the shoes behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like to run that much, you keep the shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.66,0:18:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the use of running this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This feeling...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the goal of the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to see Remi make it to the goal. Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats, for finishing the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took me over a year. Forget the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shoes wanted to come to the goal with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oy, Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wimp. Aren't you two in track and field?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem was that the truck went the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy. I can run thousand kilo more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, that's impressive. Then, you can carry me on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?! Watch your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it you wimps!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Girls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bead bracelet I had since I was a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:21:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:22:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next on Miracle Girls, "Current of Memory."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, we'll teleport to the bracelet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:08.26,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:11.56,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:14.89,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.14,0:22:18.10,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:34.75,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:38.04,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,, that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:51.55,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know it better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:57.98,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:05.03,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:11.78,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:14.70,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:20.12,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:23.17,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.63,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:29.72,song-ed,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us
